     47          /**
     48           * API007_OP_SEGMENT_LIST \n
     49           * cmd:  payload:  no payload
     50           * fdb:  payload contains a list of segment ID
     51           *
     52           * API007_OP_SEGMENT_INFO \n
     53           * cmd:  payload: byte[0] = segment id\n
     54           *
     55           */
